        "body": "<p>Scrum Club makes women's and men's rugby clothing and protective wear for players of every size, age and level. What sets us apart is an unwavering commitment to player safety: a significant share of our proceeds goes directly into research aimed at understanding and reducing the risk of injury in rugby.</p><p>Buy our kit and you get quality rugby apparel — and help make the sport safer for the next generation.</p>",
